{"tid":1632603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［點都出］政府反對司法覆核蒙面法理由之一：有效阻嚇及減少「暴力」","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:13:57.000Z","uid":173849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd142c6bc1bf138f53140d784ba937fc6b0e1a2d","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:52:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570329080914/【禁蒙面法】張建宗-除禁蒙面法外無其他及時方案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570329080914%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%99%A4%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%96%E7%84%A1%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8F%8A%E6%99%82%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=468fc4dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570329080914%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%99%A4%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%96%E7%84%A1%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8F%8A%E6%99%82%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&h=53a3af21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570329080914/【禁蒙面法】張建宗-除禁蒙面法外無其他及時方案</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌中說，激進示威者進行暴力破壞和攻擊，幾乎全部蒙面，意圖隱藏身分，有承擔的政府不能對情況坐視不理。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《禁蒙面法》旨在針對進行暴力破壞的示威者，阻嚇和減少蒙面下的暴力和不負責任的行為</span></span>，同時防止犯罪者逃避法律制裁，強調訂定《禁蒙面法》是基於社會上出現了危害公共安全的情況，絕對不是香港已進入緊急狀態。他又指法例無損市民的言論自由與和平集會的自由。市民在不使用蒙面用品的情況下，依然可自由參與公眾活動"},{"pid":"e2df8980b3cf43d2de8bdf9689794ab10c07088f","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:52:34.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69591ac50082a96e12474b9a155fb1ed869d8329","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"如果上街既人更多既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c38a130ba34b71f1017240121a3447716f8791","tid":1632603,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsuebxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsuebxZ.png&h=344e2c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城／<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場／<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙中心／黃大仙廣場／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場／<br />\n紅土黃何九：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場／<br />\n將軍澳：黨鐵Popcorn／香港單車公園／<br />\n沙田：新城市廣場／車公廟站 曾大屋遊樂場<br />\n馬鞍山：新港城／鞍誠街花園／<br />\n大埔：大埔超級城／大埔中央廣場／<br />\n上水： 上水廣場／彩園廣場<br />\n屯門：屯門市廣場／屯門政府合署／新和里球場<br />\n天水圍：嘉湖銀座／天耀<br />\n元朗：Yoho／大馬路<br />\n銅鑼灣：紀利佐治街／東角道<br />\n太古：太古城中心／鰂魚涌公園／<br />\n柴小杏：柴灣橋／柴灣公園<br />\n西區：中山公園<br />\n南區：香港仔中心／<br />\n東涌：東薈城噴水池／富東商場"},{"pid":"62439f884665f3a5cf1754c128aeb733db12fda4","tid":1632603,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20f9c5fed212f1b3ae5dea31310bd03a0b250e47","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116fd867da0a8e293a747985c0d2be22f6c175ff","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28667fff87e19f3c4a4a15c097391bc8b5cfef69","tid":1632603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:02:35.000Z","msg"